item.title: CVE-2022-1540|2024-08-03T00:10:03.363Z -- unknown -- postmagthemes%20demo%20import
item.description: The PostmagThemes Demo Import WordPress plugin through 1.0.7 does not validate the imported file, allowing high-privilege users such as admin to upload arbitrary files (such as PHP) leading to RCE.
